{"tid":2419961,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"連登一方面屌人做乜唔睇香港電影 一方面又撐燒生","createTime":"2021-02-23T15:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T04:54:36.000Z","uid":98473,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bdfdfa0765c6da4af8410d6e549fbf42785106a","tid":2419961,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"燒生未屌香港電影前又係咁話近年香港電影做得好撚好 <br />\n係你地冇人入場支持先搞到要拍合拍片<br />\n係咁叫人睇 香港電影好撚高質<br />\n宜家燒生成個廢老咁屌香港電影廢 收撚晒皮<br />\n我認同燒生 事實一定返唔返之前咁<br />\n但燒生屌幾句 你地就當人神咁話香港電影垃撚圾嫁啦<br />\n大佬 咁好心你地就一開始就咪撚浪漫主義上身<br />\n係咁叫人支持香港電影啦<br />\n明明重有一班人好努力做緊 已經行得好撚辛苦<br />\n燒生屌幾句 你地重要落井下石咁<br />\n香港人都唔支持返自己既電影 咁就真係完"},{"pid":"20eccc6cfeaf63a05f97cb837cef65a03aa94107","tid":2419961,"uid":61348,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"你可以認為香港電影業無未來<br />\n<br />\n同時支持睇港產片 兩者無衝突"},{"pid":"471bdd7c8ed0d809c88f1a7712971f556a2be0ad","tid":2419961,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20eccc6cfeaf63a05f97cb837cef65a03aa94107","tid":2419961,"uid":61348,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"你可以認為香港電影業無未來<br />\n<br />\n同時支持睇港產片 兩者無衝突"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"你睇下D人既COMMENT先啦<br />\n我都認同燒生講法 但D人踩香港電影踩到仆街"},{"pid":"24501ac1ea53e18c8dff42573e038d0c8582cbc8","tid":2419961,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f0abc2a4e1810ec6fbe9b66cf7c7d9dc09991f","tid":2419961,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ca8502bdd532e5390d0a09dd5d44e2acbef709","tid":2419961,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"